    "Noise pollution is bad for the communities that live within and around these data centers, most of which are already disadvantaged (Monserrate, 2022).",
    "Big Tech companies like Google, Facebook, and Amazon have pledged to adopt more green technology in the form of renewable energy infrastructures, but smaller-scale, traditional data centers lack the resources and capital to strive for more sustainable solutions (Hogan, 2018).",
    "In other words, this technology is not without its flaws.",
    "Researchers must be aware of the environmental costs of technological developments and push, where possible, for greener, more sustainable AI.",
    "Using LLMs in Interpretive Qualitative Research While ChatGPT and other AI-driven technologies can augment researchers' ability to analyze text (Do et al., 2022), there is very little guidance in the literature about how these technologies can be integrated into qualitative research."
